question:
What will be the output?

```js
setImmediate(()=>console.log('A'));
setTimeout(()=>console.log('B'),0);
console.log('C');
```

What will be the output?

```js
console.log('1');
Promise.resolve().then(()=>console.log('2'));
process.nextTick(()=>console.log('3'));
console.log('4');
```

What will be the output?

```js
(async()=>{
  await new Promise(res=>setTimeout(res,0));
  console.log('X');
})();
console.log('Y');
```
